# ─── Gas faucet (server-only, NO NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix) ─────────────────────────
# Bootstraps fresh judge wallets with 0.01 GAS so their first tx doesn't fail
# with "insufficient funds". Called from /api/gas-faucet via the useGasFaucet
# hook on connect. Ideally funded with ~10 GAS and isolated from the operator
# key (plan 19 §9 decision #1).
FAUCET_PRIVATE_KEY=
